{"@class": "com.nd.elearning.sdk.resource.gateway.v5.bean.question.QuestionVo", "original_type": 4, "original_sub_type": "questions", "container_id": "elearning-library_ncet-xedu_080ae380-40bc-4a84-b761-eee39249c878", "id": "ab0f91c0-4185-4628-961e-4b7dee9b97c2", "type": 201, "content": {"preview": {"question_big": "https://r1-ndr.ykt.cbern.com.cn/edu_product/esp/questions/ab0f91c0-4185-4628-961e-4b7dee9b97c2@1.pkg/1772597590704/mainbig.xml.jpg?v=1772597591573", "question_small": "https://r1-ndr.ykt.cbern.com.cn/edu_product/esp/questions/ab0f91c0-4185-4628-961e-4b7dee9b97c2@1.pkg/1772597590704/mainbig.xml.jpg?v=1772597591573"}, "identifier": "ab0f91c0-4185-4628-961e-4b7dee9b97c2", "feedbacks": [{"identifier": "showHint", "sequence": "1", "outcome_identifier": "FEEDBACK", "show_hide": "show", "content": "<p>一审题干；二审设问；三审题肢。</p>\n"}, {"identifier": "showAnswer", "sequence": "1", "outcome_identifier": "FEEDBACK", "show_hide": "show", "content": "<p>A：市场在资源配置中起决定性作用，政府是宏观调控，故A说法错误；</p>\n\n<p>B：我国相关企业的新能源技术还没有完全成熟，更没有在题干中体现领跑全球，故B说法错误；</p>\n\n<p>C：国家通过政策推动环保产品，符合可持续发展、绿色发展道路，故C符合题意；</p>\n\n<p>D：消费者因环保选择新能源汽车，体现低碳理念增强，但以旧换新基本国策不是基本国策，故D符合题意；</p>\n\n<p>故本题选C。</p>\n"}], "sequnce_number": 1, "description": "<p>（改编·2025辽宁中考真题）国家“以旧换新”政策实施以来，新能源汽车因补贴力度大且更环保，成为消费新宠。消费品“以旧换新”不仅仅是商品交易，更是一场生活方式的变革。这表明（&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;）</p>\n", "title": "（改编·2025辽宁中考真题）国家“以旧换新”政策实施以来，新能源汽车因补贴力度大且更环保，成为消费新宠。消费品“以旧换新”不仅仅是商品交易，更是一场生活方式的变革。这表明（   ）", "res_type": "$RE0201", "adaptive": false, "timer": {"timer_type": "sequence"}, "time_dependent": false, "responses": [{"identifier": "RESPONSE_1-1", "sequence": "1-1", "base_type": "identifier", "cardinality": "single", "corrects": ["C"]}], "location": "https://r1-ndr.ykt.cbern.com.cn/edu_product/esp/questions/ab0f91c0-4185-4628-961e-4b7dee9b97c2@1.pkg/item.json?v=1754710167878", "items": [{"min_choices": 0, "attachments": [], "columns": 1, "type": "choice", "choices_list": [], "associable_hotspots": [], "children": [], "hide_answer_area": false, "options